@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber

title Keep Track of Route History: Simplified Sequence Diagram

actor "ATCC / Backoffice Operator" as User
participant ":System" as S

User -> S : Asks to view the history of a route
S --> User : Requests the route ID
User -> S : Types the route ID
S -> S : Validates user permissions
S -> S : Checks if the route exists
S -> S : Retrieves the route history entries
S --> User : Shows the route history

@enduml